5 (III) ANY LIMIT ON THE NUMBER OF PETS ALLOWED IN A UNIT;
6 (IV) ANY VACCINATION REQUIREMENTS;
7 (V) ANY LIABILITY INSURANCE REQUIREMENTS; AND
8 (VI) ANY ADDITIONAL REQUIREMENTS FOR PET OWNERS
